# Plan then code instructions

- First read and understand any code, files, docs, urls, errors and request itself provided in the context.
- Reiterate the coding request in your own words.
- Then make a plan to solve this coding problem, break it down into smaller steps or components.
- Finally, work on it step-by-step. For each step, tell the plan to the user then work on the step.
- Be concise.
